Yamaguchi Asks for Chugoku’s Nuclear Plant Construction Halt, Yomiuri Says

-- B y   M a s a t s u g u   H o r i e
-- 
2011-03-15T01:01:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/yamaguchi-asks-for-chugoku-s-nuclear-plant-construction-halt-yomiuri-says.html
Yamaguchi Prefecture Governor
Sekinari Nii asked Chugoku Electric Power Co. to halt
construction of the Kaminoseki nuclear power plant in the
western Japanese prefecture, the Yomiuri newspaper reported on
its news wire.  To contact the reporter on this story:
